code: @Override protected NodeInfo<Min> info() {     return NodeInfo.create(this, Min::new, field()). }

@Override public Min replaceChildren(List<Expression> newChildren) {     if (newChildren.size() != 1) {         throw new IllegalArgumentException("expected [1] child but received [" + newChildren.size() + "]").     }     return new Min(source(), newChildren.get(0)). }

@Override protected TypeResolution resolveType() {     if (field().dataType().isString()) {         return TypeResolution.TYPE_RESOLVED.     } else {         return isNumericOrDate(field(), sourceText(), ParamOrdinal.DEFAULT).     } }
